                                                                                                                                                                                                         <!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>About</title>
    <%- include('navbar')%>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: rgb(214, 223, 241);
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .vision, .mission, .about-detail {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .heading {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #2a4d69;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vision">
        <h2 class="heading">Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          To inspire creativity and bring the beauty of nature into every home through exquisite flower paintings that evoke emotion, peace, and joy.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission">
        <h2 class="heading">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Our mission is to create unique and high-quality flower paintings that connect people with the elegance and serenity of nature, while supporting local artists and promoting sustainable art practices.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-detail">
        <h2 class="heading">About Us</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to our world of flower paintings! Each brushstroke is a celebration of nature's vibrant beauty. Our collection features handcrafted artwork that captures the delicate details and emotions of every bloom. From classic roses to exotic orchids, our paintings are a testament to the timeless charm of flowers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're looking to enhance your living space, find a thoughtful gift, or simply immerse yourself in the artistry of nature, our gallery offers something truly special.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
